"quadre groc a les captures de pantalla anteriors) independentment de la "
"configuració de l'orientació d'acoblament."

#: ../../user_interface/customizing_interface.rst:57
msgid "Adding Widgets"
msgstr "Afegir ginys"

# skip-rule: kct-library
#: ../../user_interface/customizing_interface.rst:59
msgid ""
"You can add :term:`widgets<widget>` (e.g. :ref:`view-library`, :ref:`view-"
"project_notes`) by enabling them in the :menuselection:`Menu --> View Menu`. "
"Likewise, disable them by taking off the check mark right next to their "
"entry in the menu."
msgstr ""
"Podeu afegir :term:`ginys<widget>` (p. ex. :ref:`view-library`, :ref:`view-"
"project_notes`) activant-los al menú :menuselection:`Menú --> Vista`. De la "
"mateixa manera, desactiveu-los retirant la marca de selecció just al costat "
"de la seva entrada en el menú."

#: ../../user_interface/customizing_interface.rst:65
msgid "Moving Widgets"
msgstr "Moure ginys"

#: ../../user_interface/customizing_interface.rst:67
msgid ""
"You move a :term:`widget` by grabbing the tab or the :term:`title bar` and "
"moving it to a new position. It is possible to move the widget to a "
"different position within the same panel thereby simply changing the "
"sequence of the tabs."
msgstr ""
"Moveu un :term:`giny<widget>` agafant la pestanya o la :term:`barra de "
"títol` i movent-lo a una posició nova. És possible moure el giny a una "
"posició diferent dins del mateix plafó, canviant així la seqüència de les "
"pestanyes."

#: ../../user_interface/customizing_interface.rst:69
msgid ""
"A widget can also be moved to a new panel, to its own (new) column or row, "
"or undocked as a floating window. In the example below the :ref:`Clip <ui-"
"monitors_clip_monitor>` and :ref:`Project Monitor <ui-"
"monitors_project_monitor>` widgets are being undocked and turned into "
"floating windows:"
msgstr ""
"Un giny també es pot moure a un plafó nou, a la seva pròpia columna o fila "
"(nova), o desacoblar com una finestra flotant. En l'exemple següent, els "
"ginys :ref:`Monitor de clips <ui-monitors_clip_monitor>` i :ref:`Monitor del "
"projecte <ui-monitors_project_monitor>` s'han desacoblat i convertit en "
"finestres flotants:"

#: ../../user_interface/customizing_interface.rst:76
msgid ""
"Moving Clip and Project Monitor to their own independent windows (undocking)"
msgstr ""
"Moure el monitor de clips i el monitor del projecte a les seves pròpies "
"finestres independents (desacoblament)"

#: ../../user_interface/customizing_interface.rst:78
msgid ""
"The Kdenlive layout reacts to your dragging of the widget and you need to "
"pay close attention which layout elements change color when you move over "
"them."
msgstr ""
"La disposició del Kdenlive reacciona a l'arrossegament del giny i cal posar "
"molta atenció a quins elements de la disposició canvien de color quan els "
"moveu."

